    </section>

    <section class="movement-landing__influence-section">
      <div class="movement-landing__influence-header">
        <p class="movement-landing__influence-eyebrow">Cross-era inspiration</p>
        <h2 class="movement-landing__influence-title">Movement influence network</h2>
        <div class="movement-landing__influence-intro">
          <p>See how Marvin's engineering approach intersects with Swiss suppliers, modern finishing standards, and contemporary mechanical expectations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="movement-landing__influence-layout">
        <div class="movement-landing__influence-chart">
          <div class="movement-landing__influence-chart-caption">Illustrative split of Marvin movement influence across heritage, finishing, architecture, and modern usability.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="movement-landing__influence-list">
          <article class="movement-landing__influence-card">
            <div class="movement-landing__influence-content">
              <p class="movement-landing__influence-label">Influence</p>
              <h3 class="movement-landing__influence-card-title">Marvin x Zenith</h3>
              <p class="movement-landing__influence-card-text">Shared Swiss movement vocabulary and overlapping finishing standards inform the visual genealogy.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="movement-landing__influence-card">
            <div class="movement-landing__influence-content">
              <p class="movement-landing__influence-label">Influence</p>
              <h3 class="movement-landing__influence-card-title">Marvin x Louis Moinet</h3>
              <p class="movement-landing__influence-card-text">Mechanical architecture and collector presentation echo across modern enthusiast culture.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="movement-landing__influence-card">
            <div class="movement-landing__influence-content">
              <p class="movement-landing__influence-label">Influence</p>
              <h3 class="movement-landing__influence-card-title">Technical crossover</h3>
              <p class="movement-landing__influence-card-text">Bridge shape, jewel placement, and finishing language reveal broader industry influence.</p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="movement-landing__signatures-section">
      <div class="movement-landing__signatures-header">
        <p class="movement-landing__signatures-eyebrow">Engineering details</p>
        <h2 class="movement-landing__signatures-title">Mechanical signatures</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="movement-landing__signatures-grid">
        <article class="movement-landing__signature-card">
          <div class="movement-landing__signature-content">
            <div class="movement-landing__signature-icon">S1</div>
            <h3 class="movement-landing__signature-card-title">Thin movement design</h3>
            <p class="movement-landing__signature-card-text">Elegant proportions preserve visual balance without sacrificing structural clarity.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="movement-landing__signature-card">
          <div class="movement-landing__signature-content">
            <div class="movement-landing__signature-icon">S2</div>
            <h3 class="movement-landing__signature-card-title">Engraved markings</h3>
            <p class="movement-landing__signature-card-text">Historic caliber markings reinforce traceability and collector authenticity.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="movement-landing__signature-card">
          <div class="movement-landing__signature-content">
            <div class="movement-landing__signature-icon">S3</div>
            <h3 class="movement-landing__signature-card-title">Clean architecture</h3>
            <p class="movement-landing__signature-card-text">Bridge layout emphasizes legibility and disciplined engineering rhythm.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="movement-landing__signature-card">
          <div class="movement-landing__signature-content">
            <div class="movement-landing__signature-icon">S4</div>
            <h3 class="movement-landing__signature-card-title">Precision adjustment</h3>
            <p class="movement-landing__signature-card-text">Fine regulation details support stable timekeeping and service longevity.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="movement-landing__brand-section">
      <div class="movement-landing__brand-layout">
        <div class="movement-landing__brand-copy-panel">
          <p class="movement-landing__brand-eyebrow">The Marvin caliber mark</p>
          <h2 class="movement-landing__brand-title">The Marvin caliber mark</h2>
          <div class="movement-landing__brand-text">
            <p>More than a visual cue, the Marvin caliber mark reflects our dedication to disciplined engineering, Swiss mechanical integrity, and distinctive finishing. It appears on movements that carry our standards forward.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="movement-landing__brand-badge-panel">
          <div class="movement-landing__brand-badge-circle">Marvin caliber edition</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="movement-landing__cta-section">
      <p class="movement-landing__cta-eyebrow">Continue the journey</p>
      <h2 class="movement-landing__cta-title">Experience the engineering legacy</h2>
      <div class="movement-landing__cta-text">
        <p>Explore Marvin's modern watches powered by enduring mechanical philosophy and Swiss craft.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="movement-landing__cta-actions">
        <a class="movement-landing__cta-button-primary" href="{{ section.settings.cta_button_link | default: '#' }}">
          Shop all mechanical watches
        </a>
        <a class="movement-landing__cta-button-secondary" href="{{ section.settings.cta_secondary_link | default: '#' }}">
          Download archive brochure
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Movement landing",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "section-wrapper",
  "max_blocks": 24,
  "settings": [
    { "type": "header", "content": "Colors" },
    { "type": "color", "id": "background_color", "label": "Background", "default": "#050505" },
    { "type": "color", "id": "surface_color", "label": "Surface", "default": "#0a0a0a" },
    { "type": "color", "id": "surface_alt_color", "label": "Surface alt", "default": "#111111" },
    { "type": "color", "id": "accent_color", "label": "Accent", "default": "#caa354" },
    { "type": "color", "id": "accent_secondary_color", "label": "Accent secondary", "default": "#d70f37" },
    { "type": "color", "id": "text_color", "label": "Text", "default": "#f7f2e8" },
    { "type": "color", "id": "muted_text_color", "label": "Muted text", "default": "#b9b0a3" },
    { "type": "color", "id": "border_color", "label": "Border", "default": "#24201a" },

    { "type": "header", "content": "Hero" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "hero_eyebrow", "label": "Hero eyebrow", "default": "Crafted for precision" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "hero_title_line_1", "label": "Hero title line 1", "default": "The engine" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "hero_title_line_2", "label": "Hero title line 2", "default": "Behind time" },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "hero_text",
      "label": "Hero text",
      "default": "<p>For over 170 years, Marvin has put finely tuned mechanics at the heart of every watch. From early hand-wound calibers to integrated automatic systems, our legacy breathes life into modern horology.</p>"
    },
    { "type": "text", "id": "hero_button_label", "label": "Primary button label", "default": "Discover the craft" },
    { "type": "url", "id": "hero_button_link", "label": "Primary button link" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "hero_secondary_label", "label": "Secondary button label", "default": "View movement archive" },
    { "type": "url", "id": "hero_secondary_link", "label": "Secondary button link" },

    { "type": "header", "content": "Timeline" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "timeline_eyebrow", "label": "Timeline eyebrow", "default": "Swiss horology journey" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "timeline_heading", "label": "Timeline heading", "default": "Mechanical timeline" },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "timeline_intro",
      "label": "Timeline intro",
      "default": "<p>Trace how Marvin evolved from foundational pocket-watch engineering to refined mechanical calibers designed for the modern collector.</p>"
    },

    { "type": "header", "content": "Archive" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "archive_eyebrow", "label": "Archive eyebrow", "default": "Collector reference" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "archive_heading", "label": "Archive heading", "default": "Movement archive" },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "archive_intro",
      "label": "Archive intro",
      "default": "<p>Reference the calibers, bridges, plates, and finishing details that define Marvin's mechanical language across decades.</p>"
    },

    { "type": "header", "content": "Influence" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "influence_eyebrow", "label": "Influence eyebrow", "default": "Cross-era inspiration" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "influence_heading", "label": "Influence heading", "default": "Movement influence network" },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "influence_intro",
      "label": "Influence intro",
      "default": "<p>See how Marvin's engineering approach intersects with Swiss suppliers, modern finishing standards, and contemporary mechanical expectations.</p>"
    },
    { "type": "text", "id": "chart_caption", "label": "Chart caption", "default": "Illustrative split of Marvin movement influence across heritage, finishing, architecture, and modern usability." },

    { "type": "header", "content": "Signatures" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "signature_eyebrow", "label": "Signature eyebrow", "default": "Engineering details" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "signature_heading", "label": "Signature heading", "default": "Mechanical signatures" },

    { "type": "header", "content": "Brand" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "brand_eyebrow", "label": "Brand eyebrow", "default": "The Marvin caliber mark" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "brand_heading", "label": "Brand heading", "default": "The Marvin caliber mark" },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "brand_text",
      "label": "Brand text",
      "default": "<p>More than a visual cue, the Marvin caliber mark reflects our dedication to disciplined engineering, Swiss mechanical integrity, and distinctive finishing. It appears on movements that carry our standards forward.</p>"
    },
    { "type": "text", "id": "brand_badge", "label": "Brand badge", "default": "Marvin caliber edition" },

    { "type": "header", "content": "CTA" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "cta_eyebrow", "label": "CTA eyebrow", "default": "Continue the journey" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "cta_heading", "label": "CTA heading", "default": "Experience the engineering legacy" },
    {
      "type": "richtext",
      "id": "cta_text",
      "label": "CTA text",
      "default": "<p>Explore Marvin's modern watches powered by enduring mechanical philosophy and Swiss craft.</p>"
    },
    { "type": "text", "id": "cta_button_label", "label": "CTA button label", "default": "Shop all mechanical watches" },
    { "type": "url", "id": "cta_button_link", "label": "CTA button link" },
    { "type": "text", "id": "cta_secondary_label", "label": "CTA secondary label", "default": "Download archive brochure" },
    { "type": "url", "id": "cta_secondary_link", "label": "CTA secondary link" },

    { "type": "header", "content": "Spacing" },
    { "type": "range", "id": "padding_top", "label": "Top padding", "min": 0, "max": 120, "step": 4, "unit": "px", "default": 0 },
    { "type": "range", "id": "padding_bottom", "label": "Bottom padding", "min": 0, "max": 120, "step": 4, "unit": "px", "default": 0 }
  ],
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "timeline_event",
      "name": "Timeline event",
      "limit": 8,
      "settings": [
        {
          "type": "select",
          "id": "position",
          "label": "Position",
          "options": [
            { "value": "left", "label": "Left" },
            { "value": "right", "label": "Right" }
          ],
          "default": "left"
        },
        { "type": "text", "id": "year", "label": "Year", "default": "1890s" },
        { "type": "text", "id": "title", "label": "Title", "default": "Foundation calibers" },
        { "type": "textarea", "id": "text", "label": "Text", "default": "Simple hand-wound calibers establish Marvin's early mechanical identity." }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "archive_item",
      "name": "Archive item",
      "limit": 9,
      "settings": [
        { "type": "image_picker", "id": "image", "label": "Image" },
        { "type": "text", "id": "label", "label": "Label", "default": "Series" },
        { "type": "text", "id": "title", "label": "Title", "default": "500 series" },
        { "type": "textarea", "id": "text", "label": "Text", "default": "Bridge architecture and hand-finished details designed for durability and serviceability." }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "influence_card",
      "name": "Influence card",
      "limit": 4,
      "settings": [
        { "type": "text", "id": "label", "label": "Label", "default": "Heritage node" },
        { "type": "text", "id": "title", "label": "Title", "default": "Marvin x Zenith" },
        { "type": "textarea", "id": "text", "label": "Text", "default": "Document influence, supplier overlap, or finishing philosophy related to this movement family." }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "signature",
      "name": "Signature",
      "limit": 6,
      "settings": [
        { "type": "text", "id": "icon_text", "label": "Icon text", "default": "M1" },
        { "type": "text", "id": "title", "label": "Title", "default": "Thin bridges" },
        { "type": "textarea", "id": "text", "label": "Text", "default": "Balanced bridge geometry designed for clean visual rhythm and efficient service access." }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "Movement landing",
      "blocks": [
        { "type": "timeline_event", "settings": { "position": "left", "year": "1890s - 1920s", "title": "Foundation calibers", "text": "Entry hand-wound movement platforms establish Marvin's functional architecture." } },
        { "type": "timeline_event", "settings": { "position": "right", "year": "1930s - 1940s", "title": "Dress-watch refinement", "text": "Slimmer proportions and improved finishing support elegant daily-wear designs." } },
        { "type": "timeline_event", "settings": { "position": "left", "year": "1950s - 1970s", "title": "Automatic evolution", "text": "Rotor-driven systems and improved shock protection modernize performance." } },
        { "type": "timeline_event", "settings": { "position": "right", "year": "Present day", "title": "Restored legacy", "text": "Modern Marvin designs reconnect archival engineering cues with today's enthusiasts." } },

        { "type": "archive_item", "settings": { "label": "Archive", "title": "500 series", "text": "Reliable hand-wound caliber language centered on clarity and durability." } },
        { "type": "archive_item", "settings": { "label": "Archive", "title": "700 series", "text": "Expanded bridge geometry and refined layout for improved visual symmetry." } },
        { "type": "archive_item", "settings": { "label": "Archive", "title": "900 series", "text": "A robust mechanical family balancing serviceability and elegant finishing." } },
        { "type": "archive_item", "settings": { "label": "Archive", "title": "Auto evolution", "text": "Automatic winding marks Marvin's transition into contemporary mechanical wear." } },
        { "type": "archive_item", "settings": { "label": "Archive", "title": "Tour series", "text": "Complexity-driven architecture with collector-focused details and layered finishing." } },
        { "type": "archive_item", "settings": { "label": "Archive", "title": "Base series", "text": "Foundational movements that informed later decorative and structural upgrades." } },

        { "type": "influence_card", "settings": { "label": "Influence", "title": "Marvin x Zenith", "text": "Shared Swiss movement vocabulary and overlapping finishing standards inform the visual genealogy." } },
        { "type": "influence_card", "settings": { "label": "Influence", "title": "Marvin x Louis Moinet", "text": "Mechanical architecture and collector presentation echo across modern enthusiast culture." } },
        { "type": "influence_card", "settings": { "label": "Influence", "title": "Technical crossover", "text": "Bridge shape, jewel placement, and finishing language reveal broader industry influence." } },

        { "type": "signature", "settings": { "icon_text": "S1", "title": "Thin movement design", "text": "Elegant proportions preserve visual balance without sacrificing structural clarity." } },
        { "type": "signature", "settings": { "icon_text": "S2", "title": "Engraved markings", "text": "Historic caliber markings reinforce traceability and collector authenticity." } },
        { "type": "signature", "settings": { "icon_text": "S3", "title": "Clean architecture", "text": "Bridge layout emphasizes legibility and disciplined engineering rhythm." } },
        { "type": "signature", "settings": { "icon_text": "S4", "title": "Precision adjustment", "text": "Fine regulation details support stable timekeeping and service longevity." } }
